headline.main: Dean Burmester Wins 1st European Tour Title at Tshwane Open
headline.print_headline: Dean Burmester Wins 1st European Tour Title at Tshwane Open

lead_paragraph: Dean Burmester finished with a 65 for a convincing three-shot victory at the Tshwane Open on Sunday, his maiden European Tour title.
